ro.uaic.info.optdist.internal

Class Package

  • java.lang.Object
    • ro.uaic.info.optdist.internal.Package
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PackageInterface

    @Component
public class Package
extends Object
implements PackageInterface
    Contains a static attribute, packageCount, that counts the packages as we add them and all the attributes that describe a package: a list of optionals, a year, a semester, a name and an ID.
